<p class="ql-align-justify">/法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201021/8699ce2d89be40458339b438d0353806.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>我果然还是喜欢气泡水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>————</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201021/d7bf23f6e7424dd088722a86af79aefb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">10月21日，晴。再过十来天都立冬了，广州的天气：<strong>28℃，还是那么热。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201021/d39167cc9d7749fea90ff095b5b1121a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201021/b87f3f6b57124c038af9cf57c5e0ea41.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/f6e35a067a9b47cd9b15a1665305f66f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">虽然喝过了初秋的第一杯奶茶，在广州，<strong>果然还是气泡水更香！够冰够爽</strong>，再来点果汁就更好了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201021/09db1b1a1e9f4d768fc16b49816a0502.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">咕噜咕噜喝一大口，感受<strong>气泡席卷口腔，一阵冰意从头盖到脚</strong>……我又可以了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/70801bc999c44bf9a5ae42365de1df68.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>粉色气泡水，喝完会「旺桃花」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>————</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201021/59372af9613c43338d03213b6ed30c78.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“千万别告诉别人哦！喝粉色气泡水，<strong>可以旺桃花！</strong>”闺蜜递过来的一瞬间，就被粉嫩嫩的颜色牢牢吸引。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>■ 「旺桃花」气泡水的诞生 ■</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">The birth of pink soda</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201021/ae796176ccce4e3985abce596909d211.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>新鲜感：</strong>鲜切柠檬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201021/fd0785fc170446ab8cc4b3828952a634.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>刺激感：</strong>气泡水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201021/6f77f8d7b450444fa1295e7a877fec54.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>甜蜜感：</strong>蔓越莓果汁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201021/700eebe555ab4e06bbcea75c9a40046c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>心动感：</strong>冰块撞击</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201021/7cbecb059bc34b8887ddfe4516617c60.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">粉色气泡水诞生！赶紧许愿吧，好运总是像气泡一样转瞬即逝，要牢牢抓住哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>■ 「旺桃花」气泡水的许愿方式 ■</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">The wish of pink soda</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/4845454d446147a59453035be465badc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>抿一口香水柠檬：</strong>感受暗恋的酸涩……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201021/251672441c4044d8a21bcfd757d2134d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>喝一口</strong>：酸酸甜甜冒泡泡，是恋爱的感觉！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201021/6d206ff6173e4695a26c206922a8f154.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“你怎么在这里啊，我找你好久啦~”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201021/422b0f80bbad4959a8cdfa48540d6fb0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201021/3f2293075efc4688a4c2d5dba5ebedf4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">外表和心灵，你会被哪个吸引？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>橘色气泡水，喝完…？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>————</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201021/adaa14e3bc764b19a5a543914868d478.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201021/ca53ad5436b04bce8df7b3c959f82043.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“咕咚！”好大一颗橙子！偏爱酸熘熘的女孩子注意啦，<strong>橘色气泡水，同时出道！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201021/1dc992ffc19348d5b0291e6472bdf4a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>满满橙子果汁，</strong>就像是广州永远在线的夏天，同时还加入了<strong>两片香水柠檬</strong>，赋予更丰富的口感。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201021/5611a69e531647eba5bca096e54d87dd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/e9d834080ea54f66a5ce579106b02edb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>柑橘类的香气被气泡激发，</strong>咕咚一大口，明显能感到<strong>气温骤降！</strong>冰凉酸爽，酸中还带着丝丝入扣的甜…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201021/1e1fb146bb57495d81c691507c5472b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201021/182fca8ca804411f9c5740282fc87edf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">其实脱不脱单又有什么关系呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这份橘色气泡水，<strong>和姐妹一起分享</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201021/1716e453c175495aa5fa20bd326ceecc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>90后都爱TA，00后抓紧了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>————</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201021/501f4cc27f4649679a5e143a2f8efe29.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>别问在哪里买了：TA可能就在你家楼下！</strong>00后大概不常喝，90后简直从小喝到大。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201021/184b8661fc11483dbdff0e6a129dabee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
